  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the safety and superiority of Roux-Y versus Billroth
      II gastrojejunostomy reconstruction on delayed gastric emptying after pancreatoduodenectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
